prāhurnaiguṇyaniṣṭhaṃ tadanubhajanato maṅkṣu siddho bhaveyam ||1||
traiguṇyāt-bhinna-rūpaṃ	because of the three gunas, different kinds
bhavati hi bhuvane	are indeed there, in this world
hīna-madhya-uttamaṃ yat	low, middle and high, that
jñānaṃ śraddhā ca kartā	knowledge, faith and doer
vasati:-api sukhaṃ	residence and happiness
karma ca-āhāra-bhedā:	work and food various
tvat-kṣetra-tvat-niṣevā-	Thy temple, Thy worship
ādi tu yat-iha	etc., indeed whatever there is
puna:-tvat-paraṃ	again pertaining to Thee
